# DCSS Mobile App vs Web Client: Feature Comparison

## Summary

The mobile app handles the **core gameplay loop** (map, player, messages, menus, ui-push/pop) but is missing many secondary features the web client provides. Below is a categorized breakdown.

---

## ✅ Parity — Features Present in Both

| Feature | Web Client File | Mobile App File |
|---|---|---|
| **WebSocket connection** | [comm.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/comm.js), [client.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js) | [websocket_manager.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/network/websocket_manager.dart) |
| **Login / Auth** | [client.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js) (`login_success`, [login_fail](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#497-506)) | [dcss_protocol.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/network/dcss_protocol.dart) (LoginSuccessMessage, LoginFailMessage) |
| **Map rendering** | [display.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/display.js) → [map](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/.mailmap) | [game_state.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/game/game_state.dart) → MapUpdateMessage |
| **Player stats** | [player.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/player.js) → [player](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/player.js#534-585) | [game_state.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/game/game_state.dart) → PlayerUpdateMessage |
| **Game messages** | [messages.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/messages.js) → `msgs`, [msg](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#639-644) | [game_state.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/game/game_state.dart) → GameLogMessage, GameLogBatchMessage |
| **Menus** | [menu.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js) → [menu](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#750-762), [update_menu](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#813-840), [update_menu_items](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#841-846), [close_menu](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#763-774), [menu_scroll](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#847-860) | [game_state.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/game/game_state.dart), [menu_overlay.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/ui/menu_overlay.dart) |
| **UI Push/Pop** | [ui-layouts.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/ui-layouts.js) → `ui-push`, `ui-pop` | [game_state.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/game/game_state.dart) → UiPushMessage / UiPopMessage |
| **Cursor** | [view_data.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/view_data.js) → [cursor](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/messages.js#109-129) | [dcss_protocol.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/network/dcss_protocol.dart) → CursorMessage |
| **Text areas** | [text.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/text.js) → [txt](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/ui-layouts.js#9-23) | [txt_overlay.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/ui/txt_overlay.dart) → TxtMessage |
| **Delay** | [game.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/game.js) → [delay](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#132-141) | [dcss_protocol.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/network/dcss_protocol.dart) → DelayMessage |
