| **Lobby** | [client.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js) → [lobby_entry](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#1160-1218), [lobby_clear](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#1244-1249), [lobby_complete](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#1249-1271) | [dcss_protocol.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/network/dcss_protocol.dart) → LobbyEntryMessage, etc. |
| **Game start/end** | [client.js](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js) → `game_started`, `game_ended` | [dcss_protocol.dart](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/lib/network/dcss_protocol.dart) → GameStartedMessage, GoLobbyMessage |
