## 🔶 Partial — Present but Incomplete

| Feature | What works | What's missing |
|---|---|---|
| **`ui-push`** | Generic fallback + `newgame-choice` special case | Missing **14 specific layout handlers** (describe-item, describe-monster, etc.) — all collapse to a single text-only popup |
| **Player stats** | hp, mhp, mp, mmp, ac, ev, sh, str, int, dex, place, depth, xl, gold, status | Missing: [god](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/ui-layouts.js#325-416), [title](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#661-667), `species`, `name`, `real_hp_max`, `poison_survival`, [noise](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/player.js#69-140), `adjusted_noise`, [contam](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/player.js#326-348), [time](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/client.js#1303-1324), `turn`, `wp`, `qv`, stat bars/colours, defence display |
| **Map rendering** | Tile grid with fg/bg/overlays | No [clear](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/static/scripts/chat.js#204-213) map handling, no `player_on_level`, no [vgrdc](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/minimap.js#175-182) (view grid center) |
| **Menus** | Open/close/update/scroll with hotkeys + tiles | No search ([title_prompt](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#668-747)), no [close_all_menus](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/menu.js#775-780), no rich hover/selection state |
| **Game messages** | Single and batch messages | No [rollback](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/messages.js#72-76), no `--more--`, no [text_cursor](file:///c:/Users/itsmo/dcss-mobile/tmp_crawl/crawl-ref/source/webserver/game_data/static/messages.js#109-129), no turn markers |
| **Chat** | Message parsing in protocol | No chat send UI, no chat visibility toggle |

---

## Recommended Priorities

1. **Text input system** — Blocks naming characters, searching menus
2. **`formatted-scroller`** — Blocks help (`?`), ability list (`a`), mutation list (`A`)
3. **`describe-item/monster/spell/god`** — Blocks examining anything (`x`, `v`)
4. **More player stats** (god, name, species, title, etc.)
5. **Message `--more--` and rollback**
6. **Minimap** — Very useful on mobile for navigation
7. **Monster list** — Important for tactical awareness
